'''1770'''（{{lang en|Seventeen Seventy}}），是一個位於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]的村莊，建於[[詹姆斯·庫克|詹姆斯·庫克]]第二次登陸澳洲的地點。<ref name="history">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/travel/travel-factsheet/seventeen-seventy--culture-and-history-20081121-6ds5.html|title=Seventeen Seventy - Culture and History|publisher=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2008-11-21|accessdate=2013-05-04}}</ref>此村莊亦是世界上極少數以數字作名稱的地方。<ref name="name for"/>

==名稱淵源==

1770本名朗德希爾（Round Hill）。於1770年5月24日，詹姆斯·庫克和[[努力号三桅帆船|努力号三桅帆船]]船員在此登陸。<ref name="history"/>於200年後的1970年，朗德希爾居民為了紀念詹姆斯·庫克登陸此處二百週年，故將此村莊更名為1770，即詹姆斯·庫克登陸此處的年份。<ref name="name for">{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/local/stories/2008/12/11/2444009.htm|title=Seventeen Seventy or 1770 - that is the question|date=2008-12-12|publisher=ABC Wide Bay|author=Jodie van de Wetering|accessdate=2013-05-04|archive-date=2010-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419065704/http://www.abc.net.au/local/stories/2008/12/11/2444009.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==旅遊業==
1770是一個旅遊熱點之一。1770位於一個[[半島|半島]]上，三面環[[珊瑚海|珊瑚海]]，因此成為一個水上活動熱點。此村莊亦是一個受歡迎的釣魚和衝浪地點。此村莊亦擁有一些度假住宿，餐廳，一家百貨商店，以及一個小碼頭。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.queenslandholidays.com.au/destinations/gladstone/places-to-visit/seventeen-seventy/index.cfm|title=Seventeen Seventy|publisher=Queensland Holidays|accessdate=2013-05-04|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403023839/http://www.queenslandholidays.com.au/destinations/gladstone/places-to-visit/seventeen-seventy/index.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1770節慶會於每年5月。在節慶中，居民們會模仿詹姆斯·庫克重新登陸此處，以作紀念。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.letsconnect.com.au/1770/1770festival-pp2.htm |title=The 1770 Festival |publisher=Let's Connect Australia |accessdate=2013-05-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503122500/http://www.letsconnect.com.au/1770/1770festival-pp2.htm |archivedate=2013-05-03 }}</ref>

==自然==
1770的生態環境和植被很少遭受破壞，因此這裡的自然環境亦成為了一個旅遊熱點。此村莊亦提供到達[[大堡礁|大堡礁]]、馬斯格雷夫夫人島、埃利奧特夫人島、費爾法克斯島等的導賞服務。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gladstoneregion.info/destinations/seventeen-seventy/tours/|title=Seventeen Seventy Tours|publisher=Gladstone Tourism QLD|accessdate=2013-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419042736/http://www.gladstoneregion.info/destinations/seventeen-seventy/tours/|archive-date=2013-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

這一帶附近有四個國家公園：[[深水國家公園|深水國家公園]]（Deepwater National Park）<ref name="nch">{{cite web |url=http://www.derm.qld.gov.au/parks/deepwater/culture.html |title=Deepwater National Park: Nature, culture and history |date=26 October 2010 |publisher=Department of Environment and Resource Management |accessdate=21 July 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120919232328/http://www.derm.qld.gov.au/parks/deepwater/culture.html |archivedate=2012-09-19 }}</ref>、[[埃瑞姆布拉國家公園|埃瑞姆布拉國家公園]]（Eurimbula National Park）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.experiencequeensland.com/iss/uk/regions/central-queensland/gladstone.cfm|title=Queensland , Australia - Regions|year=2010|accessdate=2010-06-19|archive-date=2012-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322151310/http://www.experiencequeensland.com/iss/uk/regions/central-queensland/gladstone.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、鬥獸場山國家公園（Mount Colosseum National Park）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.epa.qld.gov.au/projects/park/index.cgi?parkid=98 |title=Eurimbula National Park |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2006-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060620175103/http://www.epa.qld.gov.au/projects/park/index.cgi?parkid=98 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、以及朗德希爾國家公園（Round Hill National Park）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.environment.nsw.gov.au/nationalparks/parkHome.aspx?id=N0470 |title=Round Hill Nature Reserve {{!}} NSW National Parks |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2015-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401223237/http://www.environment.nsw.gov.au/NationalParks/parkHome.aspx?id=N0470 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

